title: DDFP 254: Matt 'Money' Smith & Bucky Brooks
itunes:title: DDFP 254: Matt 'Money' Smith & Bucky Brooks
description:
Shek & Rank are joined in Studio 66 by CFB 24/7 stars Matt '$' Smith & Bucky Brooks for a pre-draft marathon podcast debating the team who'd be the best fit for Johnny Football, QB prospects' body language, which team is most likely to trade up in the first round, and WAY too many other subjects to list to here. Instead, why don't you just hear 'em?
